MapGenerator.MainStructure

Class Field

  • java.lang.Object
    • MapGenerator.MainStructure.Field

  • public class Field
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents one unit of the map. This unit may hold diffrent states and has multiple owners.

    Lukas Jelinek
